Extra Practice Problems

9. In a given file, change all small letters to capital letters
10. Simillarly, change all capital letters to small letters.
11. In a given file, change first letter of every word to captial letter.
12. In a given file, change the First letter of every paragraph to Captial letter. Paragraphs can be identified by extra line breaks (as in latex).
13. Swap every adjacent pair of words in a file. Eg. Word1 with Word2, and Word3 with Word4 etc